###
```
Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DHgj5jhMJKg&list=PLjcN1EyupaQm20hlUE11y9y8EY2aXLpnv&index=1
```

```
shooter_game/
│── main.py                 # Main game loop
│── settings.py             # Game constants and settings
│── world/                  # World-related classes
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── world.py            # World class
│   └── tile.py             # Tile-related classes
│── entities/               # Game entities
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── player.py           # Player class
│   ├── enemy.py            # Enemy class
│   ├── projectile.py       # Bullets/Grenades
│   └── items.py            # Item boxes
│── ui/                     # User interface
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── buttons.py          # Button class
│   ├── healthbar.py        # Health bar
│   └── screenfade.py       # Screen transitions
│── assets/                 # Game assets
│   ├── images/
│   ├── audio/
│   └── level_data/         # Level CSV files
```

### For mac 
```
pip install py2app

Update setup.py

rm -rf build dist
python setup.py py2app
```

### For Windows
```
pip install pyinstaller
pyinstaller --onefile --windowed main.py
```